description:
So Who Is This Jesus? (1999) | Full Movie | Russell Boulter | Crawford Telfer

Two thousand years ago a man was born who changed the course of history. He was betrayed by one of his twelve followers and executed for crimes he did not commit. His name is familiar to us all -- even if only as a swear word.  But who is he -- who is this Jesus?  Russell Boulter provides answers to the question in a down-to-earth, no nonsense style.  This program has been designed specifically to help people with no previous knowledge of Jesus to have a better understanding of who He is.  For those who already know Jesus, it will give them an even greater understanding of Jesus' life and the joy of knowing him better.  Filmed in Israel, the presentation is in three parts:
I: His Story Had a Long Preparation
II: His Birth and Life
III: The Meaning of It All Jesus Christ, Story of, Russell Boulter

Director: Crawford Telfer
Starring: Russell Boulter
